WEBVTT

00:13:28.269 --> 00:13:30.281
quando avranno circa 14 anni,


00:13:30.281 --> 00:13:32.001
con le spalle voltate verso di loro,

00:13:32.001 --> 00:13:33.099
in cucina,


00:13:33.099 --> 00:13:35.466
proprio mentre stai preparando 
qualcosa per loro.

00:13:35.466 --> 00:13:36.398
(Risate)


00:13:36.398 --> 00:13:38.929
E lo stiletto psicologico va dentro.

00:13:38.933 --> 00:13:41.988
(Risate)


00:13:41.988 --> 00:13:45.493
(Applausi)


00:13:46.682 --> 00:13:50.782
E chiedi: "Come sapevi
esattamente dove conficcarlo?"

00:13:50.782 --> 00:13:51.821
(Risate)


00:13:51.821 --> 00:13:52.704
E ti dicono:


00:13:52.704 --> 00:13:54.304
"Ti ho osservato

00:13:54.304 --> 00:13:55.578
(Risate)

00:13:55.578 --> 00:13:57.218
per un bel po' di anni."

00:13:59.667 --> 00:14:05.102
